      right: ["Sudden severe abdominal pain with peritoneal signs","Shoulder pain (Kehr sign) indicating hemoperitoneum","Hemorrhagic shock: tachycardia greater than 120, hypotension, pallor","Abdominal rigidity with rebound tenderness","Syncope with positive pregnancy test"]
