      sideEffects: "Hypokalemia, hyponatremia, hypomagnesemia, metabolic alkalosis, dehydration, hypotension, ototoxicity (with rapid IV push), hyperglycemia, hyperuricemia",
      contra: "Anuria, severe electrolyte depletion with hypovolemia, hepatic coma, sulfonamide allergy (cross-sensitivity possible)",
